{"tid":1049873,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"住係太古嘅絲打要小心呢個阿叔(冇圖)","createTime":"2019-03-06T14:57:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T17:54:50.000Z","uid":171055,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"75ec18d475730c82ac9642e85aae81754b5dcfbe","tid":1049873,"uid":171055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T14:57:52.000Z","msg":"話說同老母係AEON食完飯行街，點知今日勁多人，咁啱同老母分開左，諗住睇下有咩零食，就污低身捻住拎零食，然後就突然有人摸我屎忽，我就望去後面，一望佢隻變態手就係我屎忽隔離，再望條能樣竟然係到扮無野。跟住我就一直跟住條友一邊打比我老母，最後叫左保安加報警！！！<br />\n***<br />\n呢條畜生已經多次非禮妙齡女子，每次都從多人中入手！！！<br />\n係到提醒絲打們遇到呢啲事絕對唔可以啞忍！！唔可以助長呢啲變態佬再做呢啲變態行為！！！<br />\n係到呼籲住喺太古或者成日喺太古行街嘅女孩子要小心呢條友！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xnFNSzD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxnFNSzD.png&h=c4195fb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ATQx3Gn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FATQx3Gn.png&h=22cfb70f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Arr1W12.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FArr1W12.png&h=aac2f599&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da9e6cb1c9f4bb187e330b3aa3dbd17baf99c676","tid":1049873,"uid":51436,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T14:59:06.000Z","msg":"坐監啦廢中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec21ac6a1fa9be19a883613b2747604eea12dd7","tid":1049873,"uid":82482,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T14:59:47.000Z","msg":"差佬做嘢未"},{"pid":"f6501b2af4fb28ca249d97c26f8e01ac385e1cbd","tid":1049873,"uid":115237,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T15:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xtQ95WV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxtQ95WV.png&h=7401fbdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪佢兄弟？"},{"pid":"970d23c9f665c5261ac253d84825587c207e7a7f","tid":1049873,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"reply